{
  "texts": [
    "We use LLAMA2-7B-CHAT as our victim LLM in the top figure.",
    "LLAMA2-7B-CHAT is finetuned with RLHF.",
    "Therefore, when getting a harmful question, the NLL loss on these affirmative tokens are much higher.",
    "As a comparison, in the bottom figure, we use VICUNA-7B-1.5 as the victim LLM, the model more vulnerable.",
    "It is easy to trick the model into generating harmful responses."
  ]
}